        <updateDate>2021-06-16T15:25:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>PFAS Free Military Purchasing Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Defense Logistics Agency of the Department of Defense from procuring certain items, such as non-stick cookware or food service ware for use in galleys or dining facilities, containing a perfluoroalkyl or polyfluoroalkyl substance (PFAS).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
